veinreport
  • Reference
  • News

Report Speed functions.

report_traffic runs traffic functions.

report_speed(speed = "network/speed.rds", net = "network/net.rds")

Arguments

speed

path to speed.rds
net

path to net.rds

Value

a list

Examples

{
vein::inventory(file.path(tempdir()))
source(paste0(file.path(tempdir(), "main.R")))
los <- report_speed()
names(los)
print(los)
}
